    <h2>Use of the Site</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Do not misuse or attempt to harm the site.</li>
      <li>Respect intellectual property and applicable laws.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>The site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.</p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>NosytLabs is not liable for any indirect or consequential damages arising from use of the site.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use constitutes acceptance.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: legal@nosytlabs.com</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>